25/01/2006
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- The BiH Security Ministry and UNHCR issued a joint statement Tuesday (24 January) calling on Croatian refugees residing in BiH to renew their registration by 10 February. A re-registration procedure for the refugees is currently under way. The process is aimed at settling the status of Croatian refugees in BiH and regulating their rights. (Fena, RTRS - 24/01/06)
